Query Plan
====================================
|ID|OPERATOR   |NAME|EST. ROWS|COST|
------------------------------------
|0 |INSERT     |    |0        |0   |
|1 | EXPRESSION|    |0        |0   |
====================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([__values.c1], [__values.c2], [__values.c3]), filter(nil), 
      columns([troot.c1], [troot.c2], [troot.c3]), partitions(p0)
  1 - output([__values.c1], [__values.c2], [__values.c3]), filter(nil)
      values({1, 0, -1})

insert into troot values(1, 0, -1);
EXPLAIN select c1, c2, c3, level, connect_by_iscycle, connect_by_isleaf from troot start with c1 = 1 connect by nocycle prior c1 = c2;
Query Plan
================================================
|ID|OPERATOR              |NAME |EST. ROWS|COST|
------------------------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP CONNECT BY|     |0        |89  |
|1 | TABLE GET            |troot|1        |53  |
|2 | TABLE SCAN           |troot|1        |36  |
================================================

Outputs & filters: 
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([troot.c1], [troot.c2], [troot.c3], [LEVEL], [CONNECT_BY_ISCYCLE], [CONNECT_BY_ISLEAF]), filter(nil), 
      conds([troot.c1 = troot.c2]), nl_params_(nil)
  1 - output([troot.c1], [troot.c2], [troot.c3]), filter(nil), 
      access([troot.c1], [troot.c2], [troot.c3]), partitions(p0)
  2 - output([troot.c1], [troot.c2], [troot.c3]), filter(nil), 
      access([troot.c1], [troot.c2], [troot.c3]), partitions(p0)

select c1, c2, c3, level, connect_by_iscycle, connect_by_isleaf from troot start with c1 = 1 connect by nocycle prior c1 = c2;
