| c1 | c2   | c3   | level | connect_by_iscycle | connect_by_isleaf |
+----+------+------+-------+--------------------+-------------------+
|  1 |    0 |   -1 |     1 |                  0 |                 1 |
+----+------+------+-------+--------------------+-------------------+
